             <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 group-hover:text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
                디지털 트랜스포메이션,<br>AI 도입 및 데이터 플랫폼 구축.
             </p>
          </div>
          <!-- Item 4 -->
          <div class="p-8 border-r border-slate-200 hover:bg-slate-900 hover:text-white transition group cursor-pointer">
             <span class="text-2xl mb-4 block font-serif text-slate-300 group-hover:text-white/50">04</span>
             <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">운영 혁신</h3>
             <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 group-hover:text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
                공급망 관리(SCM),<br>운영 효율화 및 비용 절감.
             </p>
          </div>
          <!-- Item 5 -->
          <div class="p-8 border-r border-slate-200 hover:bg-slate-900 hover:text-white transition group cursor-pointer">
             <span class="text-2xl mb-4 block font-serif text-slate-300 group-hover:text-white/50">05</span>
             <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">조직 설계</h3>
             <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 group-hover:text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
                조직 설계 및 성과 관리,<br>리더십 개발 및 문화 혁신.
             </p>
          </div>
          <!-- Item 6 -->
          <div class="p-8 hover:bg-slate-900 hover:text-white transition group cursor-pointer flex items-center justify-center">
             <span class="text-sm font-bold border-b border-current pb-1">전체 서비스 보기 →</span>
          </div>
       </div>
    </div>
  </section>

